title: Gross National Product, Income Estimates for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1939-1945 (2)--Seasonally Adjusted Data, 1946-1966. Data Reprgsent Gross National Product In Current Dollars Minus "Statistical Discrepancy." Data Are At Annual Rate. Source: Survey Of Current Business, 1954 Supplement, National Income.

This NBER data series q08280a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 8 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter08.html.
